        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Featuring a nail file, knife blade, scissors, and key ring, this ASR Outdoor mini pocket knife is ready for adventure; great for camping, to carry as an EDC multi-tool, to include in a bug out bag, with survival gear or an emergency preparedness kit, this little pocket knife does it all.<br/><br/>Compact and lightweight, the multi-tool pocket knife weights under a pound and measures just 2.25 inches when closed. Whether you're fishing, hunting, backpacking, camping, or prepping gear for an outdoor survival or emergency preparedness kit, include this mini ASR Outdoor pocket knife to have alongside you on your next outdoor adventure; each tool looks in place for consistent, efficient, and reliable performance and it will never ask you to sacrifice on weight or space.<br/><br/>With the included keychain ring incorporated into the design, you can attach the pocket knife multi tool to just about anything you need: backpack, wallet, belt loop, camping gear and much more depending on where work or your next outdoor excursion takes you.<br/>Available Colors: Black, Green, Purple, Blue",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
